rld:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to a city where ghostification is just another part of daily life. The atmosphere is both bleak and absurd.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Puzzle-Solving & Mental Realms:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ghosts linger not just in flesh—but in mind. Solve puzzles and dive into their inner worlds to uncover their pasts.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Narrative-Driven:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story unfolds through exploration, letting you piece together each ghost’s life—and what remains of it.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro Vibes:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel art and classic BGM give it the charm of old-school RPGs, with a gritty twist.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Systems:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save by smoking cigarettes. Restore health by sleeping. Nothing here works quite like you'd expect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/4756946f4f2fcefe356d692b0f868939.webp?t=1756042601\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/4756946f4f2fcefe356d692b0f868939.poster.avif?t=1756042601\" class=\"bb_img\" width=30 height=49 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Controls】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Z key: Confirm</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >X key: Menu / Cancel</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrow keys: Move</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shift key: Dash</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save         : Use Tobacco or Dead Cig</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Act → Sleep : Restores Energy if low</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >F5   : Toggle Fullscreen / Windowed Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  F12 :Return Title (no save)</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/5be6fb654ed6dbbfdb70535755258301.webp?t=1756042601\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/5be6fb654ed6dbbfdb70535755258301.poster.avif?t=1756042601\" class=\"bb_img\" width=18 height=30 /></picture></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Recommended for】</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Love retro-style games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy puzzle-solving and exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are drawn to story-rich RPGs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Appreciate dark humor with a lo-fi edge</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/736a97f78cc9756d74cd8ead8fbfd927.webp?t=1756042601\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201240/extras/736a97f78cc9756d74cd8ead8fbfd927.poster.avif?t=1756042601\" class=\"bb_img\" width=34 height=58 /></picture></span></p>",
